{"tid":1936913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳] 偽黃扮手足呃蝦條","createTime":"2020-03-21T14:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T17:59:54.000Z","uid":96970,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"47e9d53ac40660461edb725e705d3b16a7a30145","tid":1936913,"uid":96970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[請廣傳] 偽黃扮手足呃蝦條</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n姓名: (花名)白偉洛,(真名同音)<span style=\"color: red;\">王維聰</span><br />\n中學:聖德貞中學(中五)<br />\n生日: 2002年02月 21日<br />\n電話: <span style=\"color: red;\">+852 5715 6714, +852 5409 6799</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Whatsapp: +852 5409 6799</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcpE8Jm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcpE8Jm.jpg&h=09898b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Telegram: lokk22</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzqEpgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzqEpgP.jpg&h=682f08f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Instagram: lok_02.21</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuqkTao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuqkTao.jpg&h=10e5b0ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WAUdao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WAUdao.jpg&h=ce00ed9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nEumCB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnEumCB4.jpg&h=119dabb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6CrOJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN6CrOJK.jpg&h=c949a166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ci68hCb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fci68hCb.jpg&h=f2382ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6fuedax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6fuedax.jpg&h=d977c90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Facebook: 白偉洛</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxhzdaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxhzdaO.jpg&h=7142ea2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rR3FTaO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrR3FTaO.jpg&h=617915c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JfkAG39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfkAG39.jpg&h=d7783a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xN9qjQP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxN9qjQP.jpg&h=8b05375c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個賤男真名叫王維聰(同音), <span style=\"color: red;\">花名白偉洛/草草,佢會用呢d花名周圍呃蝦條</span>.<br />\n佢會扮前線手足然後呃金主俾錢佢住酒店,同時佢會不斷<span style=\"color: red;\">利用妹妹仔嘅同情心</span>,氹佢地上酒店.佢會講到自己好唔開心,好大壓力,無人無物,為香港付出咗好多,好需要人陪,目的就係為咗呃蝦條.<br />\n其中一個受害人X小姐俾佢利用同情心,2020年3月上旬俾佢氹咗上去酒店,地點係尖沙咀逸東酒店11樓,第一次見面冇發生到D咩.<br />\n跟住呢個賤男就KEEP住搵呢個X小姐,講到自己好攰,好需要人陪,呢個賤男就話自己單身,終於又俾佢呃多次上去.就係呢一日佢就呃咗X小姐最寶貴嘅野,完咗之後就對X小姐極冷淡<br />\nX小姐頂唔順想離開呢個賤男,點知佢就問朋友意見,就發現呢個賤男好多大話,佢話自己俾狗跟好驚,但係佢又<span style=\"color: red;\">IG PO STORY周圍去玩</span>,佢<span style=\"color: red;\">話自己單身</span>,但係就搵到佢FACEBOOK原來<span style=\"color: red;\">有女朋友</span>.跟住又發現咗原來呢個賤男唔止欺騙X小姐感情,仲<span style=\"color: red;\">呃咗好多人.</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eadOhDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeadOhDm.jpg&h=eae14ffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>10月1日</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSUBrwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSUBrwO.jpg&h=79b5149c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>11月2日真手足喺度死守CU,點知佢撚動物果D狗</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gahaYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gahaYS.jpg&h=4123e876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>11月17日理大果日</strong><br />\n<br />\n仲有關於嗰女仔，嗰女仔ig有四千幾人Follower，但一個關於文宣嘅事都冇岀現過，佢兩個都係借黃色經濟黎昆人，咩都冇做過，求其打兩個光復香港，而且721 831 101 1101 1102  1117全部無post<br />\n<br />\n好多人都唔滿意佢偽黃扮深黃前線手足.唔夠黃唔係問題,但係扮深黃扮手足呃錢呃蝦條真係天理不容!!<br />\n有個男仔為咗拎證據,佢扮女仔搵呢個賤男,跟住呢個賤男就用同樣手法呃人上酒店.有錄音為證.<br />\n<br />\n1.<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/399106178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F399106178&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92FxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=687a5fcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/399106178</a><br />\n2.<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/399106214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F399106214&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92FxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b218ce0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/399106214</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家廣傳出去!!一定有好多受害人唔敢出聲,希望你地會講番件事出黎,唔好再有女仔以為呢個男仔係深黃前線而俾佢呃咗!!"},{"pid":"efaa4e26a3dcd598f05796d85092a825552a87f5","tid":1936913,"uid":167506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"扮前線姐 未必偽黃"},{"pid":"634e5f54c30ddfa02f078233648e7875a0b3e620","tid":1936913,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"原來扮前線呃蝦條咁正<br />\n我都試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71370a2ee190bc8c9bed73e6ae4eb4e1a1c1dcf0","tid":1936913,"uid":128120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"條女都有問題啦<br />\n咁易食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1536249320a05804436ed63c13522a9245084","tid":1936913,"uid":353267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲仲仆街個留學生<br />\n推爆佢"},{"pid":"1cc35671240c4225674fc5a70bf271c2002e7d6a","tid":1936913,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,